# Void Music Player

VMP is a minimalist, keyboard-driven TUI music player designed for high-fidelity audio and distraction-free listening. Built with Go, it provides a "rice-friendly" alternative to complex setups like MPD.

## Controls

- `j/k`: Browse Folders
- `Enter`: Select & Play

- `p`: Play/Pause
- `b/n`: Prev/Next Track
- `s`: Toggle Shuffle

- `+/-`: Volume Control
- `q`: Quit

Keybinds are also shown inside the app if you forgot some :P

## Installation

Ensure you have [Go](https://go.dev/doc/install) installed and your `$GOPATH/bin` added to your `$PATH`.

```bash
go install [github.com/](https://github.com/)vmp102/void-music-player@latest
